Package: keyed
Title: Explicit Key Assumptions for Flat-File Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gilles", "Colling", email = "gillescolling@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Helps R users make implicit data assumptions explicit by attaching
    keys to flat-file data and warning when those assumptions are violated.
    Designed for CSV-first workflows without databases, schemas, or version
    control. Provides key definition, assumption checks, join diagnostics, and
    optional drift detection against reference snapshots.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/gcol33/keyed, https://gcol33.github.io/keyed/
